						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">krzysiobal wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">What's the distance between two adjacent rows of pins? 0.4&quot; ?</div><br /><br />I believe so.<br /><br />There was a mistake or two in the original post.  First, there is no need to run wires to the CPU or PPU.  D0-D4 is already available at the socket to be made by removing the BU chip.  Only three additional pins maximum are needed, and those are for output.</div>

					
